damaged belt buckles should be replaced immediately it said 
the problem is caused when the red plastic pushbutton weakens 
from prolonged exposure to radiation and heat from the sun nhtsa 
said adding this may cause the safety belt to latch improperly 
or not at all greatly increasing the risk of injury in a crash 
if a safety belt on one of the affected cars does not latch or 
release properly the car should be taken in for repair nhtsa 
