faulty electrode in the headpiece placed over taferos skull and 
that it had not been fixed 
we are still concerned that our client may literally be burned 
at the stake nolas told reporters after ms fawsetts ruling 
ms buenoano 47 is known as the black widow killer because 
of the fatal poisoning of her husband the drowning of her 
paralyzed teenage son and attempted carbombing murder of a 
boyfriend she was present for the hearing and listened and watched 
attentively but showed no emotion at any of the testimony or the 
judges ruling 
ms fawsett rejected as pure speculation the testimony by 
defense expert fred leuchter that the problems in the tafero 
execution would probably be repeated 
officials for the state department of corrections testified that 
an artificial sponge in the headpiece caused the problems they 
said it had been replaced by a natural sponge and called an 
