threatening way and had other arrests on minor charges 
in 1971 pough was arrested for investigation of murder but was 
allowed to plead guilty to aggravated assault and was given five 
years probation because his record was erased after he completed 
his probation pough could legally buy guns in florida even though 
in most cases felons may not do so under state law 
