the weeks preceding the killings 
quitaji davis said he had been firing a gun at night for two 
weeks 
a woman who had lived with him told us about two weeks ago 
that he said he was going to kill a lot of people ms davis said 
ms gadsden recalled he always said when he leaves this 
world he was going to take someone with him 
