would not be stampeded into approving such a measure during the 
visit to capitol hill next week of south african leader nelson 
mandela 
its pretty obvious what is happening here they want to have 
a bill pending when mr mandela is addressing a joint meeting of 
congress on tuesday dole told the senate 
the bill aims at overturning six jobdiscrimination decisions 
that the supreme court handed down last year 
provisions range from a ban on racial harrassment in the 
workplace to requiring employers whose hiring patterns do not 
reflect local demographics to show that their practices are 
necessary for business reasons 
the bush administration has been threatening a presidential veto 
of the measure produced by the senate labor and human resources 
committee but talks between sponsors and the administration have 
been going on with an eye toward resolving the problems 
the administration says the bill that emerged from committee 
would usher in the use of racial hiring quotas on the part of 
employers who would be fearful of lawsuits otherwise senate 
sponsors led by sen edward m kennedy dmass disagree and note 
that the measure says nothing about quotas 
mitchells move friday was not designed to shut off a filibuster 
actually in progress but to assure that no such delaying tactics 
could be used to block floor action before next weeks fourth of 
july recess 
mitchells action if approved would shut off debate on a motion 
to proceed to floor action on the bill but opponents of the bill 
could still force delay of a final passage vote until after the 
recess 
he set a vote tuesday on whether to shut off debate but left 
open the possibility that agreement could still be reached 
it is my fervent hope that we will be able to reach an 
agreement that will be satisfactory to all concerned mitchell 
said 
as a result of the negotiations he said the issues have been 
significantly narrowed on that matter and there will hopefully be 
an agreement which will permit us to act in a relatively concise 
period of time and that is of course an objective that we all 
share 
