<TEXT>
did a terrorist plant a bomb or did a missile go 
astray in an aerial dogfight was there a bungled investigation or 
an international coverup of what caused the mysterious jetliner 
crash that killed 81 people 
ten years after a dc9 on a domestic flight blew apart in 
twilight skies and fell into the sea near the tiny island of 
ustica the questions remain unanswered 
many theories have been advanced but little information has 
been revealed a complicating factor is judicial secrecy which 
forbids disclosure until the investigation leads to indictments or 
closure of the case 
in may an official panel of five experts who said in march 1989 
that a missile had struck the plane reexamined the evidence and 
split between missile and bomb 
premier giulio andreotti declared recently the more i read 
about it the less i understand its very disturbing this 
interweaving of suspicions and rumors 
a week earlier a state television report claimed authorities 
