from exports should keep the economy out of recession 
other analysts are not so confident of the intentions of the fed 
and its chairman alan greenspan 
tight money is the cornerstone of alan greenspans relentless 
campaign against inflation said h erich heinemann chief 
economist at ladenburg thalmann amp co he is following a 
highrisk strategy 
